None.

++ Protected

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_action -- The action being requested of (performed by) the application.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_action_default -- The default application action.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_action_info -- The info variables to use for actions.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_dir -- Base directory under which actions, views, etc. are located.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_info -- Application request parameters collected from the URI pathinfo.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_layout -- The name of the layout to use for the view, minus the .layout.php suffix.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_layout_dir -- Where the layout directory is located.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_layout_var -- The name of the variable where page content is placed in the layout.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_name -- The short-name of this application.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_query -- Application request parameters collected from the URI query string.

* Solar_Controller_Page::$_view -- The name of the view to be rendered after the action, minus the .view.php suffix.

